title: Like What (Freestyle)

description.plain: The renowned rapper and songwriter Cardi B has recently added “Like What” to her most recent album, CB2, as her most recent freestyle. A brilliant collaborative endeavor, the single was composed by Timbaland, Missy Elliott, and Cardi B. The song, which was produced by DJ SwanQo, Sean Island, OctaneThisThatGas, and Lateef the Truthspeaker, combines sounds and lyrics flawlessly to create a cadence that will have you grooving. Do not pass up the opportunity to listen to this Cardi B masterpiece, which will leave you wanting more.
